Burden of early, advanced and metastatic breast cancer in The Netherlands.

Vondeling GT(1), Menezes GL(2), Dvortsin EP(3), Jansman FGA(4)(5), Konings 
IR(6), Postma MJ(3), Rozenbaum MH(7).

Author information:
(1)Department of Pharmaco-Epidemiology and Economics, University of Groningen, 
