Can cardiovascular magnetic resonance prompt early cardiovascular/rheumatic 
treatment in autoimmune rheumatic diseases? Current practice and future 
perspectives.

Mavrogeni SI(1), Sfikakis PP(2), Dimitroulas T(3), Koutsogeorgopoulou L(4), 
Katsifis G(5), Markousis-Mavrogenis G(6), Kolovou G(6), Kitas GD(7).

Author information:
(1)Onassis Cardiac Surgery Center, 50 Esperou Street, P. Faliro, 175-61, Athens, 
Greece. soma13@otenet.gr.
(2)First Department of Propaedeutic and Internal Medicine, National and 
Kapodisstrian University of Athens Medical School, Athens, Greece.
(3)4th Department of Internal Medicine, Hippokration University Hospital, 
Medical School, Aristotle University of Thessaloniki, Thessaloniki, Greece.
(4)Pathophysiology Department, National and Kapodisstrian University of Athens 
