Exploring the need for Transition Readiness Scales within cystic fibrosis 
services: A qualitative descriptive study.

Bourke M(1), Houghton C(2).

Author information:
(1)HRB Clinical Research Facility Galway, National University of Ireland Galway, 
Galway University Hospitals, Galway, Ireland.
